<MudFileUpload T="IBrowserFile" OnFilesChanged="@UploadFile" Accept=".png,.jpeg" Hidden="@false" @ondragenter="@SetDragClass" @ondragleave="@ClearDragClass" @ondrop="@ClearDragClass" @ondragend="@ClearDragClass" InputClass="absolute mud-width-full mud-height-full overflow-hidden z-10" InputStyle="opacity:0; cursor:pointer;">
  <ActivatorContent>
    @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(value: _base64Image))
    {
      <img src="@_base64Image" width="50" height="50" alt="Imagem do utilizador"/>
    }
    else
    {
      <MudText>Adicione a foto aqui.</MudText>
    }
  </ActivatorContent>
</MudFileUpload>
